title: Detroit Red Wings Justin Abdelkader Leads @NHL Stars Of Week
text:
Press Releases Detroit Red Wings Justin Abdelkader Leads @NHL Stars Of Week 
DETROIT, Michigan – Justin Abdelkader shared the NHL lead with four goals and made the Detroit Red Wings game winning goal, in a 4-0 victory over the Toronto Maple Leafs on Octobet 9th. Detroit Red Wings Justin Abdelkader, New York Rangers center Oscar Lindber and Arizona Coyotes goaltender Mike Smith nave been name the NHL “Three Stars” for the Week ending on Octobet 11th, 2015.
